<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="l12 m12 s12">
      <div class="content-wrap">
        {{#if is_en}}
          <h1>Calculator</h1>
        {{else}}
          <h1>계산기</h1>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="l3 m6 s12">
      <div class="content-wrap calculator-wrap">
        {{#if is_en}}
          <h3>Select a country.</h3>
        {{else}}
          <h3>나라를 선택하세요.</h3>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="sublist_foldable relative" data-open="false">
          <div class="folder" id="country_list">
            <span class="list_header">
              {{#if is_en}}List of Countries{{else}}국가 목록{{/if}}
            </span>
            {{#if is_en}}
              <span>List of Countries</span>
            {{else}}
              <span>국가 목록</span>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="l3 m6 s12">
      <div class="content-wrap calculator-wrap" id="income-input" data-show="false">
        {{#if is_en}}
          <h3>Enter your income.</h3>
        {{else}}
          <h3>수입을 입력하세요.</h3>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="calculator-input-wrap">
          <input type="number" class="calculator-input" id="calculator-income" />
          <span id="currency"> USD</span>
        </div>
        <button onclick="calculate()">
          {{#if is_en}}Calculate{{else}}계산하기{{/if}}
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="l6 m12 s12">
      <div class="content-wrap calculator-wrap" id="calc-result" data-show="false">
        {{#if is_en}}
          <h3>Based on your income, the amount of your greenhouse gas emission is ... </h3>
          <p class="helper">You can change profession sector in the below select box.</p>
        {{else}}
          <h3>수입에 기반한 당신의 온실가스 배출량은 ...</h3>
          <p class="helper">아래 선택 박스에서 직업군을 변경할 수 있습니다.</p>
        {{/if}}
        <div id="calc-result-sector">
          <select id="calc-result-sector-selector" onchange="change_sector()">
            <option value="tot" selected>{{#if is_en}}General{{else}}일반{{/if}}</option>
            <option value="agr">{{#if is_en}}Agriculture{{else}}농업{{/if}}</option>
            <option value="mnf">{{#if is_en}}Manufacturing & Construction{{else}}제조건축업{{/if}}</option>
            <option value="eng">{{#if is_en}}Energy{{else}}에너지산업{{/if}}</option>
            <option value="tsp">{{#if is_en}}Transport{{else}}수송{{/if}}</option>
            <option value="etc">{{#if is_en}}Others{{else}}비제조산업{{/if}}</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <h3 class="calc-equiv">{{#if is_en}}And it's equivalent to{{else}}그리고 다음과 같은 양입니다.{{/if}}</h3>
        <div id="calc-result">
          <div id="calc-result-emit">
            <div class="emoji">🌫</div>
            <div class="title">{{#if is_en}}Emmissions{{else}}{{/if}}</div>
            <div class="value"></div>
            <div class="content"></div>
          </div>
          <div id="calc-result-driving">
            <div class="emoji">🚗</div>
            <div class="title">{{#if is_en}}Distance Driven{{else}}{{/if}}</div>
            <div class="value"></div>
            <div class="content"></div>
          </div>
          <div id="calc-result-bulb">
            <div class="emoji">💡</div>
            <div class="title">{{#if is_en}}Fluorescent Bulb{{else}}{{/if}}</div>
            <div class="value"></div>
            <div class="content"></div>
            <p class="helper">
              {{#if is_en}}1 falsh indicates 1 day.{{else}}1번 깜빡임은 1일입니다.{{/if}}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="helper">
          {{#if is_en}}
            Fuel Efficiency: 11.1km/l (28 mpg) (combined, TOYOTA Camry XLE 2.5-Liter/4-Cylinder/6-Speed-Automatic, <a href="http://www.toyota.com/camry/features.html#!/mpg/2540" target="_blank">Source</a>). Flurescent Bulb: 5 Watt per hour. Specific calclation rates from US Energy Protection Agency (<a href="http://www.epa.gov/cleanenergy/energy-resources/refs.html" target="_blank">Source</a>)
          {{else}}
            연비: 11.1 km/l(복합, 도요타 캠리 XLE 2.5CC/4기관/6단자동변속, <a href="http://www.toyota.com/camry/features.html#!/mpg/2540" target="_blank">출처</a>). 형광등: 시간 당 5 와트. 자세한 환산비율은 미국 에너지보호청 US Energy Protection Agency (<a href="http://www.epa.gov/cleanenergy/energy-resources/refs.html" target="_blank">출처</a>)을 참고했습니다.
          {{/if}}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://d3js.org/d3.v5.min.js"></script>
<script src="/hmde/js/hmde_utility.js"></script>
<script src="/hmde/js/calculator_control.js"></script>
<script>
  create_country_list('#country_list', "{{ln}}");
  $('.sublist_foldable')
    .on('mouseover', function() {
      $(this).attr('data-open', 'true');
    })
    .on('mouseout', function() { 
      $(this).attr('data-open', 'false');
    });
</script>